Comparing Indices

Note for user regarding this R Notebook:

This notebook compares all indices to one another. In order to knit the document fully, we must first include all the code to build the indices (including loading and subsetting the data, re-leveling the variables, and building the MCA models), as the comparison plots reference the values generated by the MCA models. These pieces of code will make the notebook longer to knit, but will not appear in the output file.
